{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Case","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO22MenuLinkIterSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","title":"MenuLinkIterSignalName.notify","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuLinkIterSignalName\/notify"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuLinkIterSignalName"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menulinkitersignalname\/notify"]}],"references":{"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"type":"link","url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"canonical parameter names","type":"text"}],"title":"canonical parameter names","identifier":"#c